node.text: God dang! Twin Turbos and superchargers are just a match made in heaven. And you all thought we was gonna break it I mean we might but not yet lol

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Westen champlin in Cowley County, Kansas. May be an image of 2 people, car and outdoors.

node.text: New Video live On YouTube! Absolute epic video we spent alot of time and hard work on it. And it's probably my favorite Video we have ever made. I never imagined in my wildest dreams I would be able work with @dodgeofficial and actually sit down and have a conversation with The Ceo of dodge! Also got to meet @therealtavarish super cool guy he's awesome @throtl @alextaylorracing @ericchrishon All super good people go watch and see how the race unfolded.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Westen champlin on August 14, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text:
We Made it to Roadkill Nights! And GUYS this Twin Turbo Hellcat is so freaking awesome. Honestly we went into this event believing we would be dead last.

 I mean we ain't Drag Racers and We are new to it but I had some of the best Guys I have met From @hptuners @barthtuning and @hellionturbo to help us make this Car Fast And we went out on the Track with no testing.

And damm did it Surprise us its a freaking Frieght Train and has so much insane power. @igniteracingfuel

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Westen champlin in Cowley County, Kansas. May be an image of 1 person, standing and outdoors.

node.text: I had the great idea that I was gonna rescue this Charger and drive it to Roadkill nights! But I Ran outta time before the Event. It might have been for the best just to much MERICA at one time might be a bad thing lol @roadkillshow @dodgeofficial #motortrend @davidfreiburger @finnegan999

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Westen champlin in Winfield, Kansas. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text: New Video live On YouTube. Guys We turned our freaking Free Hellcat into a God dam Fighter plane! And On top of that We put TWIN Turbos on this bad boy. Now we have A 6.2L Supercharged Twin Turbocharged Hemi and this Unit is so fast the Air Force And FAA calls me every time I even start it up lol. @dodgeofficial @roadkillshow @therealtavarish @alextaylorracing @throtl @motortrend

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Westen champlin in Cowley County, Kansas. May be an image of 1 person and cake.

node.text: Today Is my birthday and I am 23 years old. Did we eat too much cake? Of course! did we have to much fun... NEVER lol. Guys I was surrounded by friends and family and made a bunch of horsepower. It was a good one!

node.text:
New Video LIVE on YouTube! So @dodgeofficial gave me a Widebody Hellcat Redeye! To modify however we want to drag Race at Roadkill Nights on Woodward Ave in Michigan So obviously the 1st thing I had to do was put Bull Horns on it for more Areodynamics lol.

 I never thought I would get the opportunity to be in this event and just have to thank the guys at @dodgeofficial and @roadkillshow Aug 14th on Woodward Ave come out and see us

node.text: BIG ANNOUNCEMENT: Guys we got invited by @dodgeofficial @motortrend and @roadkillshow to attend Roadkill Nights! AND Drag race I have always been a massive fan of Roadkill and remember watching the 1st Roadkill nights event they ever had. I never thought I would have the ability or opportunity to be in something like this but here we are! And I am super excited for this event Aug 14th is the date save it come out we need as much Redneck support as we can get lol.
